---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import Navbar from "../components/Navbar.jsx";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="IT Strategy & 1–5 Year Technology Roadmap Planning | Aurora ICT"
  page="services"
  description="Strategic IT roadmap planning and technology advisory. Aurora ICT delivers 1-year, 3-year and 5-year IT strategies covering infrastructure, cybersecurity, SaaS platforms and scalable growth planning."
>
  <Navbar client:load />

  <main class="page-main">
    <section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-16 md:py-20">
      <div class="glass rounded-3xl glow p-8 md:p-10">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold text-white">
          Strategic IT Roadmap &amp; Technology Planning
        </h1>
        <p class="mt-4 text-lg md:text-xl" style="color: var(--muted);">
          Aurora ICT helps organisations move from reactive IT decisions to a business-aligned technology strategy. We deliver 1-year, 3-year and 5-year IT roadmaps grounded in a full assessment of your current environment, operating risks, cost profile, resilience requirements and growth objectives.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4 text-base md:text-lg" style="color: var(--muted);">
          Our approach is independent, vendor-neutral and outcome-focused. The goal is simple: design the right technology future for your business with clear priorities, scalable decisions and measurable outcomes.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4 text-base md:text-lg" style="color: var(--muted);">
          If your team is currently operating in a reactive pattern, start with <a href="/insights/from-reactive-it-to-a-clear-roadmap" class="underline decoration-white/30 hover:decoration-white text-white">From reactive IT to a clear roadmap</a> for context on why sequencing and governance matter.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 pb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-white">What We Deliver</h2>
      <div class="mt-6 grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-3">
        <article class="glass rounded-2xl glow p-6">
          <h3 class="text-white font-extrabold text-xl">1-Year Stabilisation &amp; Risk Reduction</h3>
          <p class="mt-3" style="color: var(--muted);">
            Immediate improvements, risk mitigation, cybersecurity uplift and optimisation of existing infrastructure.
          </p>
        </article>

        <article class="glass rounded-2xl glow p-6">
          <h3 class="text-white font-extrabold text-xl">3-Year Growth &amp; Optimisation Strategy</h3>
          <p class="mt-3" style="color: var(--muted);">
            Scalable architecture planning, SaaS rationalisation, cybersecurity maturity uplift and cost optimisation aligned with business expansion.
          </p>
        </article>

        <article class="glass rounded-2xl glow p-6">
          <h3 class="text-white font-extrabold text-xl">5-Year Strategic Technology Vision</h3>
          <p class="mt-3" style="color: var(--muted);">
            Long-term infrastructure evolution, digital transformation planning, resilience architecture and future-ready technology frameworks.
          </p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>



    <section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 pb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-white">What You Gain From a Structured IT Roadmap</h2>
      <p class="mt-4" style="color: var(--muted);">A practical strategy that improves executive visibility, reduces risk exposure and supports controlled growth.</p>
      <div class="mt-6 grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
        <article class="glass rounded-2xl glow p-6">
          <p style="color: var(--muted);">Clear technology priorities aligned to business goals.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="glass rounded-2xl glow p-6">
          <p style="color: var(--muted);">Reduced operational risk and fewer surprise incidents.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="glass rounded-2xl glow p-6">
          <p style="color: var(--muted);">A practical cybersecurity uplift plan with measurable steps.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="glass rounded-2xl glow p-6">
          <p style="color: var(--muted);">Smarter IT investment planning and cost control over time.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="glass rounded-2xl glow p-6">
          <p style="color: var(--muted);">Scalable architecture and platforms that support growth.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="glass rounded-2xl glow p-6">
          <p style="color: var(--muted);">A vendor-neutral plan tailored to your environment without fixed solutions.</p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 pb-12">
      <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-8">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-white">Comprehensive IT Environment Assessment</h2>
        <p class="mt-4" style="color: var(--muted);">We assess your entire IT ecosystem, including:</p>
        <ul class="mt-4 list-disc pl-6 space-y-2" style="color: var(--muted);">
          <li>Infrastructure &amp; Architecture</li>
          <li>Network &amp; Connectivity</li>
          <li>Cloud &amp; SaaS Platforms</li>
          <li>Cybersecurity Posture</li>
          <li>Business Continuity &amp; Disaster Recovery</li>
          <li>Cost Structure &amp; Risk Exposure</li>
          <li>Compliance Readiness</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 pb-12">
      <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-8">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-white">Who This Is For</h2>
        <p class="mt-4" style="color: var(--muted);">This service is ideal for:</p>
        <ul class="mt-4 list-disc pl-6 space-y-2" style="color: var(--muted);">
          <li>Growing small to medium businesses</li>
          <li>Organisations outgrowing their current IT structure</li>
          <li>Businesses preparing for expansion or compliance uplift</li>
          <li>Companies frustrated with reactive IT support</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 pb-12">
      <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-8">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-white">Why Aurora ICT</h2>
        <ul class="mt-4 list-disc pl-6 space-y-2" style="color: var(--muted);">
          <li>Independent and vendor-neutral advice</li>
          <li>Business-aligned technology decisions</li>
          <li>Structured roadmap methodology</li>
          <li>Strategic advisory capability similar to a Fractional CTO</li>
          <li>Focus on long-term outcomes, not quick fixes</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 pb-12">
      <div class="glass rounded-2xl glow p-8 md:p-10">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-white">Roadmap FAQs</h2>

        <div class="mt-6 space-y-6">
          <article>
            <h3 class="text-white font-extrabold text-xl">What do you deliver in a Digital Roadmap?</h3>
            <p class="mt-2" style="color: var(--muted);">
              We deliver a current-state assessment, prioritised initiatives, and a sequenced 12, 36, and 60-month plan with risks, dependencies, and practical next steps across architecture, network, platforms/SaaS, and cybersecurity.
            </p>
          </article>

          <article>
            <h3 class="text-white font-extrabold text-xl">How long does the assessment and roadmap take?</h3>
            <p class="mt-2" style="color: var(--muted);">
              Typically 2–4 weeks depending on complexity and stakeholder availability.
            </p>
          </article>

          <article>
            <h3 class="text-white font-extrabold text-xl">Do you recommend specific vendors or products?</h3>
            <p class="mt-2" style="color: var(--muted);">
              Our advice is vendor-neutral and options-based, with recommendations guided by fit, outcomes, and constraints rather than fixed solutions.
            </p>
          </article>

          <article>
            <h3 class="text-white font-extrabold text-xl">Can you work with our existing IT provider or internal team?</h3>
            <p class="mt-2" style="color: var(--muted);">
              Yes. The roadmap complements existing providers and internal teams, supporting coordination and clear execution.
            </p>
          </article>

          <article>
            <h3 class="text-white font-extrabold text-xl">What size organisations is this suited for?</h3>
            <p class="mt-2" style="color: var(--muted);">
              It is ideal for growing SMBs and mid-sized organisations, especially teams needing structure before scaling or major change.
            </p>
          </article>

          <article>
            <h3 class="text-white font-extrabold text-xl">What do you need from us to get started?</h3>
            <p class="mt-2" style="color: var(--muted);">
              We need stakeholder goals, high-level architecture and inventory access, a SaaS list, security posture notes, current pain points, and key constraints such as budget and timeline.
            </p>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 pb-24">
      <div class="glass rounded-2xl glow p-8 md:p-10 text-center">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-white">Book a Strategic IT Assessment</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-base md:text-lg" style="color: var(--muted);">
          Contact us to start building your structured IT roadmap.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-3 text-base md:text-lg" style="color: var(--muted);">
          Explore more practical guidance in <a href="/insights" class="underline decoration-white/30 hover:decoration-white text-white">Aurora ICT Insights</a>.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-6 flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-4">
          <a
            href="/contact"
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 rounded-xl font-extrabold transition hover:brightness-110"
            style="background: var(--color-accent-green); color: #08110c; box-shadow: 0 0 22px rgba(57,255,122,0.22);"
          >
            Contact Aurora ICT
          </a>
          <a
            href="/it-consulting"
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 rounded-xl font-bold border border-white/15 bg-white/10 hover:bg-white/15 transition text-white"
          >
            Explore IT Consulting
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
